id":2296713,"uid":13645,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb34b512a6d0c2fcc8014b593504b3ac2b41334","tid":2296713,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:47:36.000Z","msg":"望鏡預要cut嗰條線有足夠嘅前後空位<br />\n打燈，扭少少軚，起油"},{"pid":"2df2576e3c2936537c2562f1a3fdec5dd2dcc9f2","tid":2296713,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"cut線扭軚唔使多，起油更重要"},{"pid":"6468df03e3002a57764f69262119e15206a1501e","tid":2296713,"uid":269954,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"5fc79846db591288a04dbd91f75839f89ea40df1","tid":2296713,"uid":339384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"各位ching 絲打<br />\n<br />\n請問cut 線要有咩注意<br />\n<br />\n點先為之一個好嘅cut 線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"Cut 完對方唔洗收油唔洗落 brake<br />\n<br />\n對佢完全無影響就為之靚<br />\n<br />\n每一次 cut 線都係獨立情況<br />\n<br />\n佢距離可能遠但佢車速又可能快<br />\n<br />\n點 cut 法先唔影響到佢<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下<br />\n<br />\n有可能係 brake 減速等佢過左，喺佢後面 cut<br />\n<br />\n又可能係比油喺佢前面 cut<br />\n<br />\n總之唔影響到對方為前題<br />\n<br />\n如果喺前面 cut 完但你令到對方(同你之間)唔夠安全兩秒而佢焗住收返慢去拉長個距離，咁理論上呢個都唔係最靚最 perfect 嘅 cut 線"},{"pid":"f48348541d52f9dad7efabc097e2b8009937d174","tid":2296713,"uid":339384,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6468df03e3002a57764f69262119e15206a1501e","tid":2296713,"uid":269954,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"5fc79846db591288a04dbd91f75839f89ea40df1","tid":2296713,"uid":339384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"各位ching 絲打<br />\n<br />\n請問cut 線要有咩注意<br />\n<br />\n點先為之一個好嘅cut 線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset