sets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:28:21.000Z","msg":"brake 住cut 係戇鳩，但係1823 點會入到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7151deeb5e96ddaa887c91f0ae1838f17f188b2f","tid":2296713,"uid":262200,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:40:24.000Z","msg":"買架二百萬以上嘅車<br />\n只要夠貴又夠快<br />\n就全世界都讓你"},{"pid":"a817157af03906e87ff5746cbad4af52e2816112","tid":2296713,"uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T19:52:53.000Z","msg":"我會預返CUT 完線, 同後車有返最小2秒距離我先會CUT<br />\n見FB 好多片, 快線車, 等到同隔離車有3-4秒距離先CUT返入中線. 就俾人話快線撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7985671e852ada3c4e3a348946818490a50d60e","tid":2296713,"uid":89182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T20:38:57.000Z","msg":"confirm clear就一氣呵成去做<br />\n唔係嘅話本來無事都拖到有事<br />\n<br />\n平時慢線cut中可能大家差距都係+10km左右，好易判斷<br />\n<br />\n你試下小路出啲尤其100km limited highway<br />\n<br />\n就更易感覺到車速同距離，以後拿捏就更準<br />\n<br />\n因為匯合前條小路果陣你可能得3-50km<br />\n後面上緊嚟架車有番差上下距離車速可以80-90km<br />\n<br />\n呢啲情況就要睇後車車距+車速<br />\n仲要決定埋你架車扭力/你對腳狠唔狠"},{"pid":"5e5305b98f0d06191ba75ba8930ed3578d819fac","tid":2296713,"uid":5650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T23:22:59.000Z","msg":"一早望定鏡 打燈 再望鏡 望盲點 比油cut<br />\n唔該真係要打燈 人地讓你就讓你 唔讓等下架<br />\n成日有柒頭cut線唔撚打燈又唔夠距離一野斬埋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外記得望一望盲點 有時d 26就係正你隔離"},{"pid":"17b35bdbd4097ea8486736efef6a3922ba6a14b6","tid":2296713,"uid":18899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"死板油cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9ff39861a6857d59d871593df038b1383a2951","tid":2296713,"uid":198375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T00:40:43.000Z","msg":"cut線就大油出 咪撚慢吞吞等轉數上<br />\n架車係渣唔撚係錫<br />\n<br />\n我後面dup一dup拉撚